<i>that finally bloody kills you. </i>

77
00:05:58,422 --> 00:05:59,840
John Nash?

78
00:05:59,924 --> 00:06:01,550
Hello.

79
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:03,260
Charles Herman.

80
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:05,137
Pleased to meet you.

81
00:06:14,563 --> 00:06:16,857
PLAYER: [Outside] All right! Well done!

82
00:06:22,071 --> 00:06:25,157
CHARLES: Well, it's official.
I'm almost human again.

83
00:06:25,991 --> 00:06:29,453
<i>Officer, I saw the driver who hit me. </i>
<i>His name was Johnny Walker. </i>

84
00:06:32,706 --> 00:06:34,541
Whew.

85
00:06:35,417 --> 00:06:37,962
CHARLES: Well, I got in last night
in time for...

86
