You're not easily distracted, are you?

90
00:06:50,474 --> 00:06:52,977
- I'm here to work.
- Are you? Right.

91
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,853
I see. Crikey!

92
00:07:04,989 --> 00:07:06,907
