- Currency exchange?

188
00:12:25,981 --> 00:12:27,733
You know, food.

189
00:12:29,276 --> 00:12:31,946
You have no respect for cognitive reverie,
you know?

190
00:12:32,029 --> 00:12:34,406
Yes. But pizza...

191
00:12:36,075 --> 00:12:38,702
Now, pizza I have enormous respect for.

192
00:12:40,537 --> 00:12:42,581
And, of course, beer.

193
00:12:48,337 --> 00:12:50,256
I have respect for beer.

