...but could we assume
that I've said all that?

212
00:14:41,117 --> 00:14:44,079
Essentially we're talking about
fluid exchange, right?

213
00:14:44,162 --> 00:14:46,373
So, could we just go straight to the sex?

214
00:14:47,958 --> 00:14:49,834
Oh, that was sweet.

215
00:14:50,752 --> 00:14:52,837
WOMAN: Have a nice night, asshole!

216
00:14:53,338 --> 00:14:55,049
NEILSON: Ladies, wait!

217
