00:16:00,281 --> 00:16:02,950
Do you see what they're doing there?

237
00:16:05,369 --> 00:16:07,663
PROFESSOR 2:
Congratulations, Professor Max.

238
00:16:07,747 --> 00:16:10,374
MAX: Thank you, sir. Thank you.

239
00:16:11,543 --> 00:16:13,003
It's the pens.

240
00:16:13,378 --> 00:16:17,424
Reserved for a member of the department
that makes the achievement of a lifetime.

241
00:16:17,966 --> 00:16:19,843
Now what do you see, John?

242
00:16:21,011 --> 00:16:22,721
